<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>At the moment FlashMessenger only supports a numeric array of messages.
It would be usefull to be able to specify a handle for a message:</p>

<p>$this-&gt;_flashMessenger-&gt;addMessage('There was an error validating your form', 'error');</p>

<p>The second parameter is the handle, so when I want to assign the error message to my view, I can do this:</p>

<p>$this-&gt;view-&gt;error = $this-&gt;_flashMessenger-&gt;getMessage('error');</p>

    </div>
